{"tid":91217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【「亞硝酸鈉」作醃料引發命案】【商販：知有危險但誰會跟錢作對？】","createTime":"2017-01-22T16:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T16:36:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce942a14061918dadca8c820a2e1faca3fbcfdf5","tid":91217,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:25:46.000Z","msg":"河南有個開鹵肉店的商販，日常為了讓肉質更嫩、色澤更紅，以「亞硝酸鈉」醃肉，用剩的放在家。<br />\n<br />\n但沒想到妻子吃火鍋時用了「亞硝酸鈉」，經搶救幾天後不治。<br />\n<br />\n原來食用「亞硝酸鈉」 3 克以上即可致命，醫生表示急症室不時接收「亞硝酸鈉」中毒個案，懷疑與市面醃肉有關。<br />\n<br />\n有商販稱行內用「亞硝酸鈉」十分普遍，市面多間調味店異口同聲表示知道對身體有害，但亦反問誰會跟錢作對？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/615414278650644/?hc_ref=NEWSFEED\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F615414278650644%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DNEWSFEED&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgyaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=f242ed2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/615414278650644/?hc_ref=NEWSFEED</a>"},{"pid":"b996d7bd04f756802e1f7cf12f030917709e834e","tid":91217,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051b3b5edc2b790e4c4bdddd71ae58eb5c397736","tid":91217,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"商販明知「亞消酸納」有危險，只是要賺黑心錢，不得以而為之。<br />\n但，問題是，<br />\n(一) 為什麼會带回家 ? 商販是「在家中醃肉的嗎 ? <br />\n(二) 就算一定要放在家中，有危險的東西都會告戒家人注意，何來「誤用」? <br />\n(三) 案中只憑商販自己一人供詞，謂妻子自行取食中毒，而且當時商販並不在場(亦無不在場証㯫) 。太方便了罷 ?"},{"pid":"1bb93c2dbb6f9bf5f1d98e5fdea5376f48b2edb9","tid":91217,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"其實恐怖得來好悲哀，大陸現在的人為了錢可以毫無道德可言，死的係你家人不是自己家人，當出了事之後才發現原來真係有報應，但仍然不知悔過"},{"pid":"bf0dce573af14e9c80d7ce660fefa4ce912383a4","tid":91217,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265043c2e622e4556b5ab7efbecf4a1dd0a0b2da","tid":91217,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T17:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c237c16fc87b8240a5b0bf6073cfb76b1a0f21","tid":91217,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T18:46:22.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"768a507febb032a5e0adb9a3bc4e98f754f62c3c","tid":91217,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T19:33:33.000Z","msg":"亞硝酸鈉唔係話全世界內類加工食物都有用既咩？<br />\n<br />\n腸仔、午餐肉、臘腸？？只要控制係某個範圍內就無事架嘛好似<br />\n<br />\n但係佢放向屋企就真係抵死啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32a0001cced04272f0466eae235bc6e703b47d6","tid":91217,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T19:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>亞硝酸鈉唔係話全世界內類加工食物都有用既咩？<br />\n<br />\n腸仔、午餐肉、臘腸？？只要控制係某個範圍內就無事架嘛好似<br />\n<br />\n但係佢放向屋企就真係抵死啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntrue. 點會spam同ham係粉紅色就係因為加左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個dose要控制得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋不嬲都叫你地食少啲咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80eaca7c6442c59b4fb75a7a78fa925383e7793b","tid":91217,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T19:54:26.000Z","msg":"但沒想到妻子吃火鍋時用了「亞硝酸鈉」，經搶救幾天後不治。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee177b7dca38caab955bcb350d8e7e52a994b5c3","tid":91217,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>亞硝酸鈉唔係話全世界內類加工食物都有用既咩？<br />\n<br />\n腸仔、午餐肉、臘腸？？只要控制係某個範圍內就無事架嘛好似<br />\n<br />\n但係佢放向屋企就真係抵死啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq